567  lemma of_nat_sub {n m : ℕ} (h : m ≤ n) : of_nat (n - m) = of_nat n - of_nat m :=
id                           ┴       ┴ ┴ ┴    └────┘  ┴ ┴ ┴  ┴ └────┘ ┴ ┴ └────┘ ┴
src                          ┴         ┴      └────┘    ┴    ┴ └────┘   ┴ └────┘
typ                          ┴       ┴ ┴ ┴    └────┘  ┴ ┴ ┴  ┴ └────┘ ┴ ┴ └────┘ ┴
568  show of_nat (n - m) = of_nat n + neg_of_nat m, from match m, h with
id        └────┘  ┴ ┴ ┴  ┴ └────┘ ┴ ┴ └────────┘ ┴             ┴  ┴
src       └────┘    ┴    ┴ └────┘   ┴ └────────┘

569  | 0, h := rfl
id             └─┘
src            └─┘
typ            └─┘
570  | succ m, h := show of_nat (n - succ m) = sub_nat_nat n (succ m),
id     └──┘ ┴            └────┘  ┴ ┴ └──┘    ┴ └─────────┘ ┴  └──┘
src    └──┘              └────┘    ┴ └──┘    ┴ └─────────┘    └──┘
